summary: I hope everyone going to tonight's show has an amazing time, and aren't focused solely on meeting Taylor. If it happens, it...
body: I hope everyone going to tonight’s show has an amazing time, and aren’t focused solely on meeting Taylor. If it happens, it happens. If it doesn’t, don’t let it ruin your experience. Meet up with friends, make new ones, and enjoy the moments that will last your whole life. You and however many thousands of people all get to spend an evening with @taylorswift . That’s pretty amazing, in and of itself. You all rock, and I’m amazed by each and everyone of you every day.
